data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Welcome, Home to a Fabulous, Country, Lakefront 3/2 home, and 2 1/2 bath home on 5 ACRES fenced with a 50 ft barn, guest house, chicken coop, dog kennel area, two ponds, and 2 pastures where you can escape the busy life and enjoy the peacefulness of a country setting. Bring the big boy toys as this land is NOT DEED Restricted! Enter through the gated entrance with a freshwater-stocked fish pond. This country home is set under a canopy of shady oak trees. This unique one-of-a-kind designed house has 1902 square feet of living area, offering two full bedrooms plus an office or possibly a 3rd bedroom, all including a private screened porch overlooking the lake and mature tree. This property is perfect for equestrian support staff housing as each bedroom has a separate entry. ( only .5 tenths of a mile from Terranova Equestrian Center) One of the three screened patios/porches has a connecting ¼ acre chain link fence for a dog run/kennel area or for sheep/goats. The second patio/porch has an 8-person heated spa. The 3rd patio /porch is accessed through the dining room or master bedroom and it looks over the front pond. Interior features offer a split plan with a living room, barstool counter, open kitchen, skylights, wood cabinetry, and an indoor Laundry Room off the 2-car garage. The master bedroom suite includes a gas fireplace between the bedroom and bath. The master bath has a jacuzzi tub, heated towel drawer, and dual sinks with plenty of closet space. In the master closet, there is a stack washer/dryer for delicate clothes. This is not anything like city living! Perfect for equestrian staff housingYou'll find a great setup for a small RANCHETTE for chickens with an existing coop plumbed with fresh water and an enclosed chicken run. Enjoy the added convenience of the 30 x 50 metal barn on a poured concrete slab, a built-in workshop with electricity, and a partial loft. The barn has plenty of room for hay, mowers, tools, boats, RV's, etc. The 800 Sq.ft. the guest house has two bedrooms for overflow guests. Like a good party? This house is MADE for entertaining. This is a MUST-see home if want to Escape City Life for a Serene Country Life!
